data.description: This charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath home sits on an oversized (1/4 acre) corner lot in Columbia Lakes. This desirable Kendall "Sherman" floor plan has a large country front porch and was built in 2019. Step into the foyer and find gorgeous 16” custom tile throughout the home.  To the left are French Doors inviting you into your study or formal dining room.  The kitchen features Espresso kitchen cabinets, granite countertops and pendant lighting.  The breakfast nook is surrounded by windows, overlooking the backyard.  This is a great home for entertaining with the kitchen open to the family room, and a fireplace with a stone hearth. Head into the primary suite (large enough for king size furniture) and you will find a gorgeous en suite bath with comfort height double vanities, a separate walk in shower and soaking tub. Extra features: New 10x12 storage shed (electricity available), Hot Tub, Plumbing for a water softener system and is set up with a Generator Plug.  Make an appointment today!
